{"tid":1593844,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[燒春袋] 9.29 10.1唔用赤納粹，仲可以用呢樣大家冇乜點留意，但中共驚得要死嘅野","createTime":"2019-09-25T09:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T16:11:32.000Z","uid":270506,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f47917e4d352e8a2a0b5ec50a9ec4c3f3469b243","tid":1593844,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:06:34.000Z","msg":"就係中華民國國旗 -<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <span style=\"color: blue;\">青天</span>白日<span style=\"color: red;\">滿地紅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4VvsSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4VvsSL.jpg&h=3b058cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(文宣由巴打 假如我不是真的 製造）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解高舉青天白日滿地紅旗=燒春袋：</span></strong><br />\n中共驚呢面中華民國國旗驚得要死，唔比台灣喺國際場合用呢面旗，電視全部blur 青天白日滿地紅，因為中華民國只要一息尚存，中共隨時都係非法叛亂政權。<br />\n<br />\n青天白日滿地紅被中共同黑警打壓例子：（Source: Wikipedia)<br />\n神州青年服務社在公眾場所活動中揮舞中華民國國旗常遭遇打壓，如在2008年台灣總統大選舉行時，團體在旺角行人專用區直播總統大選開票情況，但老社員事前被中共人民政府駐特別行政區聯絡辦公室施壓，表明不希望看到青天白日滿地紅旗，「連佈景板遣詞用字也欲知道，不太接受佈景板印有『中華民國』字眼。」[1]<br />\n<br />\n前社長林偉棠先生指當時直播時，警察給予「溫馨提示」，以「擔心團體取出青天白日滿地紅旗會與其他人引起衝突」為由，阻止他們揮動中華民國國旗。團體中有人慾取出旗幟揮舞遭警察干預，支持者即時收回，但到最後宣佈結果時，支持者也不理會警察，取出大堆中華民國國旗舞動，警察也無可奈何。<br />\n<br />\n你可能會話台灣人未必會鐘意呢面旗，但我地用呢面旗係攞黎針對中共最驚嘅痛處，以及世界各國都係以呢面旗黎識別台灣。最近台灣接連同兩國斷交，呢個時候高舉中華民國國旗亦可同時聲援台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我敢保證呢個歷史場面喺香港重現會係極震憾，將會係對中共莫大嘅羞辱：</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNBiBPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNBiBPV.jpg&h=f3f38f3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GiPsu9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGiPsu9W.jpg&h=6e06952b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好同埋美國國旗一齊高舉，以示當年中華民國-美國嘅邦交係義利並重，唔似得而家中共-美國關係只係建基於利益<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vxxGhi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vxxGhi.jpg&h=cf0b1c67&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vchasXj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvchasXj.png&h=a36cc02d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd70677fa854f3b07db5d872fe86e582e805c7a6","tid":1593844,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"b87c22a006df4571a65430a30484ccc4178df855","tid":1593844,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:10:03.000Z","msg":"P 牌仔推唔到post, 請大家幫手幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9af5a7d271daf62481dba60ead1f5a9a57a8f5b","tid":1593844,"uid":270506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:12:25.000Z","msg":"【十月行動討論】抵制十一，歡慶雙十，全民贈慶！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21902ff67c92020b87b908220fabca2b705be163","tid":1593844,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91864a347aaa65aa47c3a422926f2394a4fa4b67","tid":1593844,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"我係美國人啊hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8235573f45b75f5b141b6307cf11f9f4174117d8","tid":1593844,"uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">赤納粹旗 比個大X就得啦，洗咩搞咁多野</span>"},{"pid":"68775ec6cd7a9dd301350555ed0520cb7d4e5516","tid":1593844,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8235573f45b75f5b141b6307cf11f9f4174117d8","tid":1593844,"uid":140326,"like":4,"dislike":1,"s